summary:
A certified linguist, foreign language teacher, translator from English into Russian and from Russian into English, with over 12 years of experience in translation, localization and teaching English and Russian.

Areas of expertise include:
- games localization
- apps localization
- website localization
- marketing texts and press-releases writing (English and Russian) and translation
- translations in oil, energy and gas 
- literary translations
- technical documents (IT, software) translation
- education (early learning, new technologies in learning, teaching English)
- copywriting (English and Russian)
- linguistics
- gamification
